{
  "id": "RAW_ffc4751a",
  "title": "GLM-5.1 开源：零介入，交付整套的 Linux 桌面系统",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247515208&idx=1&sn=8c3b1d670f76dd7f309efb609b4cb63c",
  "date": "2026-04-08 03:04:00",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bbcc7350&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FjXSGuwJvpdgiaa8HPwO35m4kO9rASF835tChDIuz2XYRs9CGuoM2ntkdUclvSs2PyD8vUrxTJYVQnByhuoB6LxxruNAxFvAN5JWzaN57NHHE%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.02);padding:0;\">\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 16px 12px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#cf4436;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">PRODUCT</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px 16px 8px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天，智谱开源了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">GLM-5.1：744B</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;参数，</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">40B</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;激活</span>，MIT 协议</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">零人工介入，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">能独立工作超过 8 小时</span>，GLM-5.1 从零交付了一套完整的 Linux 桌面系统：窗口管理器、文件浏览器、终端、文本编辑器、系统监视器、游戏库等，共计 4.8MB</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">8小时，构建Linux 桌面系统</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">SWE-Bench Pro&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">58.4</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，超过 GPT-5.4 和 Claude Opus 4.6，全球最高</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#cf4436;font-weight:700;line-height:1.9;margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">三项编码基准综合平均，全球第三、开源第一</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5907407407407408\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f9a59fc3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdia8W5sLP0MNtL4NDpEicu5WFIlLLnQiaIhsL2ib8p24DiaggEUbzWVoX9WBXqXcSscKbkqVE75zJw7eLL26eZ4wdeCAYJS40icVdDKM%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">三项编码基准综合平均分</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px 8px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">给更多时间，真的会更好</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5.1 能够在长时间任务中持续保持有效工作，这让它可以做到以前短对话里做不了的事情。以下是两个硬核的例子</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 16px 32px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">自主优化一个搜索引擎，连续跑了 655 轮</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 搜索和推荐系统的背后都有一个向量数据库，它的查询速度直接决定用户体验。GLM-5.1 用 Rust 从零写了一个向量搜索引擎，然后自己反复跑测试、看结果、改代码，连续迭代了 655 轮</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">向量数据库 655 轮优化</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">过程中模型完成了 6 次结构性的策略跳跃，从全库扫描一路优化到两级路由 + 提前剪枝，最终把查询速度从 3108 QPS 提升到&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">21472 QPS</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，提高了 6.9 倍</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"324\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdiazEOfa57gI0MsoibKibNHY7PyskPxoBeQahDvYAduktnezZkVkpR2CLsI2uefxaHJ0iaNQDjtGjIFicicxCHF8KdGIanRpMJBf39M0/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-imgfileid=\"100031547\" data-ratio=\"0.5933147632311978\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2154\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=516eb0ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdiazEOfa57gI0MsoibKibNHY7PyskPxoBeQahDvYAduktnezZkVkpR2CLsI2uefxaHJ0iaNQDjtGjIFicicxCHF8KdGIanRpMJBf39M0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">向量数据库优化轨迹：阶梯型跳跃模式</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">给 50 个 AI 模型写加速代码，跑了 1000 多轮</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">KernelBench 给模型一个挑战：拿到 50 个真实 AI 模型（MobileNet、VGG、MiniGPT、Mamba 等）的 PyTorch 代码，想办法写出运行更快的 GPU 版本，功能完全一样但速度要快</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"273\" data-backw=\"546\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ae4176d2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FjXSGuwJvpdia2Eicuf5KKpXiaycakVCXN8UDqHV19gWicZbJITAicyR5RqtmGJuURJgSvKnaBLZm5VIqjyUuyVhLVticZFgtWMJa70YIVmAYKBicAQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">KernelBench Level 3 优化曲线：四个模型对比</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5.1 在 1000 多轮工具调用中自主编写了 Triton 和 CUDA 加速代码，最终达到&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">3.6 倍加速</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，远超 PyTorch 自带优化器 torch.compile 的 1.49 倍</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px 8px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">Benchmark 详细数据</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5.1 的提升集中在编码和智能体两个维度，提升幅度在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">19%-42%</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;之间。推理能力和 GLM-5 基本持平，和 Gemini 3.1 Pro、GPT-5.4 还有明显差距</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7175925925925926\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"392\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bac49e7c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdiaKXdmR78Rl2p7oKJExgg3Iv5SYJYRYgsUmia0uTECNtExHwZ9AtVgnVZRpDvtTNyeuBIPzJSYFzhicR1esCzFFiabBIlodUrwogo%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5.1 Benchmark 总览</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 16px 32px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">编码能力</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">SWE-Bench Pro</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;衡量的是模型能否在真实 GitHub 仓库中定位并修复高难度工程 Bug，是目前最接近真实软件开发的单项指标。GLM-5.1 得分 58.4，全球最高，超过 GPT-5.4（57.7）和 Claude Opus 4.6（57.3）</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">NL2Repo</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;要求模型根据自然语言描述从零构建完整的代码仓库，测试的是系统级工程能力。GLM-5.1 得分 42.7，vs GLM-5 的 35.9，提升 19%。和 Claude Opus 4.6（49.8）还有 7 分差距</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Terminal-Bench 2.0</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;让模型在真实终端环境中解决系统管理、运维和开发任务。GLM-5.1 得分 63.5，vs GLM-5 的 56.2</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">CyberGym</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是网络安全编码基准，要求模型完成渗透测试、漏洞分析等安全工程任务。GLM-5.1 得分 68.7，vs GLM-5 的 48.3，提升 42%，进步最大的单项</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"736\" data-backw=\"546\" data-ratio=\"1.348148148148148\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=260e8ee8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdgjpnLXSicJrrd0f97JUhk9fvTzCt1zEiaj9qaJED0MDpQO6eHmWmjzKPlQgPhc8ObTY2eJBl1qyHvjbV6QPwsftV6E3w7PcIOCQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">编码能力详细对比</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">智能体能力</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">BrowseComp</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;测试模型能否通过自主浏览网页解决复杂信息检索问题。GLM-5.1 带上下文管理得分 79.3</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">τ³-Bench</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在模拟客服场景中测试对话式 Agent 的双向控制能力。GLM-5.1 得分 70.6</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">MCP-Atlas</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;衡量模型在多步骤工作流中调用外部工具（MCP 服务器）的能力。GLM-5.1 得分 71.8</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vending Bench 2</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;让模型经营一年的模拟自动售货机生意，测试长期规划和资源管理。GLM-5.1 最终账户余额 $5634，vs GLM-5 的 $4432。和 Claude Opus 4.6（$8017）还有明显差距</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"736\" data-backw=\"546\" data-ratio=\"1.348148148148148\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=136ea70b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdgN1b22MjYPSEkUm0fdibuSpWRDGM9lmDVdQDKQ2z5PvzvTWrOxMkicY9mwcOOnjRibLDyLdzry41rq9qVWJQJzbZZPvaFMaibFiaJc%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">智能体能力详细对比</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">推理能力</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">HLE</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;被称为「人类最后的考试」，由各领域专家出题，专门测试模型的知识和推理极限。GLM-5.1 得分 31.0，和 Gemini 3.1 Pro（45.0）、GPT-5.4（39.8）有明显差距</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">AIME 2026</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是美国数学邀请赛 2026 年赛题。GLM-5.1 得分 95.3，各家模型在这项上已经非常接近</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">GPQA-Diamond</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是由博士级专家出题的科学问答，涵盖物理、化学、生物等领域。GLM-5.1 得分 86.2</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">推理维度整体和 GLM-5 持平，GLM-5.1 的提升集中在编码和智能体</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"594\" data-backw=\"546\" data-ratio=\"1.087962962962963\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4b8dede2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdjIHXc5sVMRb1kM7bUvnjZE9EdNHAj5QXDFtf29wFZhrIZqiblbVcWj4yqR1UQ2Aa805R0XYGfMAm7YjO7dWegpCVV5KoT5Q0EE%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">推理能力详细对比</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px 8px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术报告解读</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5.1 的技术细节沿用 GLM-5 的论文框架，论文已公开在 arXiv（2602.15763）。这里提取几个和长程能力直接相关的核心要点</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"338\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdgYBnXJaFgfianbMu5LBFPsKbpqmjunPe1YgOficvdTKftH4EBMZ1nWOPjUOfibMOdHZFdmN8LUsk3G6PVM08be4C6WyJkiaQVicu58/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"307\" data-imgfileid=\"100031548\" data-ratio=\"0.6188212927756654\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2104\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6bea6fb4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdgYBnXJaFgfianbMu5LBFPsKbpqmjunPe1YgOficvdTKftH4EBMZ1nWOPjUOfibMOdHZFdmN8LUsk3G6PVM08be4C6WyJkiaQVicu58%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 16px 32px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">异步 RL 基础设施</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"307\" data-backw=\"546\" data-ratio=\"0.5622489959839357\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-w=\"996\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=95ca0a11&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdjDIgYwWFjx7g6wwZCXgC753Rm0ANn0BqVFWfdEBmtK5O8QN8HtrYIfs95GkviaaXDmB00dyFRyefvYL35UDC4yeDupEbEl33bk%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5 整体训练管线</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统同步 RL 处理 Agent 任务时 GPU 空闲严重，因为不同任务的轨迹长度差异极大。智谱把训练引擎和推理引擎解耦到不同 GPU 设备上：推理引擎持续生成轨迹，达到阈值后批量送训练引擎更新模型，权重定期同步</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过一个「多任务 Rollout 编排器」支持超过 1000 个并发 rollout，每个任务实现为独立的微服务，注册到中央编排器统一调度</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">TITO（Token-in-Token-out）</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">异步 RL 中一个容易被忽视的问题：把推理引擎当作黑箱只取最终文本，训练器需要重新分词来重建轨迹。分词边界的微小不一致会在数千步的 Agent 任务中逐步累积</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">TITO 直接消费推理引擎产出的 token ID 流和元数据，保持 action 级别的精确对应，消除重新分词带来的误差</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">DSA 与 RL 的适配</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"326\" data-backw=\"546\" data-ratio=\"0.596989966555184\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-w=\"598\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=043cf177&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdhokGiaTckvriaKiadXnfpL4Xu0icp1epXgibdM1C1Wbsh4efotpkcYFUaGGLxxxtD92ykA08oVlUjQCrg927jo3XhbyEm3DNG0cCibA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">DSA 训练 SFT loss 对比</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5 在预训练阶段引入 DSA（DeepSeek Sparse Attention），用动态稀疏注意力把长上下文的注意力计算降低约 1.5-2 倍</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 RL 阶段出现了一个实践发现：DSA 的 indexer 必须使用确定性的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">torch.topk</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。非确定性的 CUDA 实现会导致 RL 训练几步之后 entropy 急剧下降，性能严重退化</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">双侧重要性采样</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">异步 RL 中不同轨迹可能由不同版本的模型生成，off-policy 问题严重。传统方案需要维护历史策略检查点来计算重要性采样比率</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">智谱的做法更直接：直接用 rollout 时的 log-probability 作为行为策略的代理，用 token 级别的双侧裁剪机制控制信任域，超出区间的 token 从梯度计算中屏蔽。不需要跟踪历史策略</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">环境规模</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"341\" data-backw=\"546\" data-ratio=\"0.6246418338108882\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-w=\"698\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=553f4b2e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdia6RavoBNqyTNI3O3MwS699FkFHibWTMnbQgmLe4k3onicz1WDZr6VK4tkRaziclRKK6PfFK42xZtCJoJic8RYG1CXwtUJyQqMoiaIQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">BrowseComp 上下文管理策略对比</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">编码任务：构建超过&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">10000</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;个可验证训练环境，覆盖 Python、Java、Go、C、C++、JavaScript、TypeScript、PHP、Ruby 9 种语言</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">搜索任务：构建 Web 知识图谱，从 200 万+ 高信息网页中抽取实体和关系，合成高难度多跳 QA 对</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">国产芯片全栈适配</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5 从第一天起就完成了七家国产芯片平台的全栈适配：华为昇腾、摩尔线程、海光、寒武纪、昆仑芯、沐曦、燧原</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">在华为昇腾上通过 W4A8 混量化、Lightning Indexer 融合算子、MLAPO 预处理优化等手段，单节点性能接近双卡国际集群</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">开源与使用</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5.1 权重以&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">MIT</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;协议开源，提供 BF16 和 FP8 两个版本。支持 vLLM、SGLang、xLLM（华为昇腾）、Ktransformers 本地部署</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">API 方面，GLM-5.1 已纳入&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM Coding Plan</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（Max/Pro/Lite 套餐），支持 Claude Code、OpenCode、Kilo Code、Roo Code、Cline 等工具接入</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5.1 即将上线 chat.z.ai</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考材料</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5.1 Blog</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://z.ai/blog/glm-5.1\" target=\"_blank\">https://z.ai/blog/glm-5.1</a></span></code></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5 Technical Report</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.15763\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.15763</a></span></code></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GitHub</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-5\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-5</a></span></code></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugging Face</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/zai-org/GLM-5.1\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/zai-org/GLM-5.1</a></span></code></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">ModelScope 魔搭社区</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-5.1\" target=\"_blank\">https://modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-5.1</a></span></code></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM Coding Plan</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://z.ai/subscribe\" target=\"_blank\">https://z.ai/subscribe</a></span></code></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">BigModel 开放平台</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/text/glm-5.1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/text/glm-5.1</a></span></code></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱 AI 开源 GLM-5.1 模型，凭借 744B 参数和异步 RL 等技术突破，在 SWE-Bench Pro 等编码基准测试中夺得全球第一。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱 AI 开源 GLM-5.1 模型，凭借 744B 参数和异步 RL 等技术突破，在 SWE-Bench Pro 等编码基准测试中夺得全球第一。",
  "summary": "智谱 AI 正式开源 GLM-5.1 大模型，该模型拥有 744B 总参数及 40B 激活参数，采用 MIT 协议。GLM-5.1 的核心优势在于长程任务的自主执行能力，能够独立工作超过 8 小时并从零交付 Linux 桌面系统。在技术层面，它引入了异步 RL 基础设施、TITO（Token-in-Token-out）机制、DSA 稀疏注意力适配以及双侧重要性采样等创新，显著提升了编码和智能体（Agent）能力。评测显示，其 SWE-Bench Pro 得分 58.4，位居全球首位，但在通用推理能力上与 GPT-5.4 等顶尖模型仍有差距。此外，该模型已完成多家国产芯片的全栈适配。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GLM-5.1 在编码和智能体维度实现跨越式提升，SWE-Bench Pro 夺冠。",
      "explanation": "通过长程任务优化，模型在修复真实 GitHub 仓库 Bug 的测试中得分 58.4，超越了 GPT-5.4 和 Claude Opus 4.6，展现出极强的工程实践能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "引入异步 RL 基础设施与 TITO 机制，解决 Agent 训练效率与精度问题。",
      "explanation": "通过解耦推理与训练引擎实现高并发轨迹生成，并利用 Token-in-Token-out 消除重新分词误差，支撑了模型在长达 1000 轮迭代中的稳定性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "全栈适配国产芯片，单节点性能逼近国际主流集群。",
      "explanation": "模型已适配华为昇腾、摩尔线程等七家国产平台，通过量化和算子融合优化，在昇腾芯片上实现了极高的运行效率。"
    }
  ],
